txt.en: 'From my observations, it is clear Ungoledain society is matriarchal, and those highest in the social ladder are the priestesses of Mam Murgwid. We should find and defeat them to sow confusion in their ranks.'

'From my observations, it is clear Ungoledain society is matriarchal, and those highest in the social ladder are the priestesses of Mam Murgwid. We should find and defeat them to sow confusion in their ranks.'
Legolas has asked you to defeat any Ungoledain priestesses you find in Cadar Skûs, as they are the ones who claim leadership of the clan.
You have defeated the highest ranking Ungoledain at Cadar Skûs.\n\nYou should talk to Legolas.
Legolas has asked you to defeat Ungoladan devoted in Cadar Skûs.
'Those that devote themselves to the worship of Ungwetári will forever be our enemies. If they ever learn this lesson, the bloodshed can be spared.'
